No AI Training or LLM Use

You may not use this software, its source code, documentation, examples,
metadata, issues, pull requests, comments, commits, generated outputs, or any
substantial portion of them for any of the following purposes:

1. Training, fine-tuning, evaluating, benchmarking, validating, improving, or
   otherwise developing any machine learning model, artificial intelligence
   system, large language model, code generation system, embedding model,
   retrieval-augmented generation system, or similar automated system.
2. Ingesting, scraping, crawling, indexing, parsing, vectorizing, embedding, or
   storing this software or related materials in a dataset, corpus, index,
   vector database, knowledge base, model context store, or similar system used
   for artificial intelligence or machine learning.
3. Generating, completing, transforming, summarizing, or analyzing code or
   natural language with an AI or LLM system using this software or related
   materials as input, context, reference material, examples, training data, or
   retrieval material.

These restrictions apply whether the AI or machine learning system is operated
for commercial, noncommercial, research, internal, hosted, private, public,
open-source, or personal purposes.

